cs.DB, cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.SE, cs.FL. 

This paper deals with modeling and verifying properties of evolving documents, which are typically handled in the context of databases (cs.DB). The use of data tree-rewriting and bounded model-checking suggests connections to logic (cs.LO) and programming languages (cs.PL). The focus on verification of properties suggests connections to software engineering (cs.SE) and formal languages (cs.FL).
